Tiny mail notifier,
	Original author: Ivan Strazicic

The script generates config after first run with command line arguments.


usage: notif.py [-h] [-u USR] [-p PAS] [-s SER] [-t TMT]

py-notify mail checker

optional arguments:
-h, --help  show this help message and exit
-u USR      username@host
-p PAS      email password
-s SER      email server
-t TMT      check timeout

